Installation / Config
#########################

1) Copy files from "copy_this" to your shop


#####
2) Add the following module-entries in your configuration

oxcmp_user => marm/codelogin/marm_codelogin_oxcmp_user
oxuser => marm/codelogin/marm_codelogin_oxuser


#####
3) Run 'marm_codelogin_setup.sql' 


#####
4) Adjust your templates 

a) to call the new Loginbox

i) 	Basic-Theme
	in _right.tpl change
		[{oxid_include_dynamic file="dyn/cmp_login_right.tpl" ...}]
	to
		[{oxid_include_dynamic file="dyn/marm_codelogin_right.tpl" ...}]
	
ii) Azure-Theme
	in header.tpl change 
		[{include file="widget/header/loginbox.tpl"}]
	to
		[{include file="widget/header/marm_codelogin_loginbox.tpl"}]
			
b) or build your own login-template with the new function 'login_codelogin'
